                <div class="box-step step1">
                    <span>01</span>
                    <div class="text">Download
                        <a href="data/mi-data/bulkpurchase-pk.xls">‘Application Form’</a>. Fill in your company details along with your bulk order requirement and email at wholesale@tronsmart.pk</div>
